title: NEW PATCH 9.10

embed.description: Meow meow meow. Meow mew. Meow cat meow mew 9.10, mewo. High-res versions of Yuumi's base and release skin splash art are available on League Displays! Q cast time removed, adjusted target scanning. W cast time removed. E no longer grants AD while not on cooldown. R movement speed increased and adjusted.

body:
DESTROY MASTER YI DESTROY RUNS CONQUER.ADD BUFF BRAND!!wWHY? brand was too op why buff???

replies.body:
What a strange contradiction. 

Master Yi only got nerfed for the lower ranks, but you also say that Brand is OP, and he's only a problem in the lower ranks too. You're mad that a noobstomp champion got changes to make him less noobstompy, but also mad that a noobstomp champion got buffed?

> exaggeration:
the fact of making something seem larger, more important, better, or worse than it really is
